Montecristo is a name that is etched forever in the pantheon of cigar greats. From its humble beginnings in Cuba to the modern-day Dominican version, it is considered worldwide as one of history’s finest cigars. This delicious Dominican Montecristo is the standard to which all other mellow cigars are held. It features aged Dominican tobaccos for its filler and binder, and a delectable Connecticut leaf for its wrapper. It is smooth and creamy with notes of almonds, cedar, and a slight hint of sweetness.
